{
  "video_id": "yjtCDgjxRAw",
  "title": "A forgotten ancient grain that could help Africa prosper | Pierre Thiam",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12580.0,
      "end_time": 15716.0,
      "text": "I was born and raised in Dakar, Senegal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15740.0,
      "end_time": 20756.0,
      "text": "and through a combination of accidents and cosmic justice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20780.0,
      "end_time": 22676.0,
      "text": "became a chef in the US."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22700.0,
      "end_time": 24476.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24500.0,
      "end_time": 26100.0,
      "text": "When I first arrived in New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26940.0,
      "end_time": 30396.0,
      "text": "I began working in these restaurants -- different types of restaurants --"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30420.0,
      "end_time": 33116.0,
      "text": "from French bistro to Italian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33140.0,
      "end_time": 35600.0,
      "text": "global ethnic to modern American."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36100.0,
      "end_time": 37356.0,
      "text": "At the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37380.0,
      "end_time": 41100.0,
      "text": "New York was already well-established as a food capital of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41900.0,
      "end_time": 43100.0,
      "text": "However ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44620.0,
      "end_time": 50355.0,
      "text": "with the exception of a few West African and Ethiopian mom-and-pop eateries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 50380.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "there was no such thing as African cuisine in the entire city."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55580.0,
      "end_time": 57760.0,
      "text": "Early in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57100.0,
      "end_time": 60760.0,
      "text": "I was influenced by Senegal&#39;s first president,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60100.0,
      "end_time": 61700.0,
      "text": "Léopold Sédar Senghor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 62820.0,
      "end_time": 65360.0,
      "text": "nicknamed, \"the poet president,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 65600.0,
      "end_time": 67396.0,
      "text": "who talked about a new humanism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67420.0,
      "end_time": 68796.0,
      "text": "a universal civilization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68820.0,
      "end_time": 74836.0,
      "text": "in which all cultures would come together around a communal table as equals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74860.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "each bringing its own beautiful contribution to share."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79500.0,
      "end_time": 82860.0,
      "text": "He called it \"the rendezvous of giving and receiving.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84200.0,
      "end_time": 86316.0,
      "text": "That concept resonated with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86340.0,
      "end_time": 88260.0,
      "text": "and it has guided my career path."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 89300.0,
      "end_time": 92396.0,
      "text": "After years of working in restaurants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92420.0,
      "end_time": 95556.0,
      "text": "I yearned for my work to have a deeper impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 95580.0,
      "end_time": 98980.0,
      "text": "that would go beyond the last meal I had served."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100420.0,
      "end_time": 103356.0,
      "text": "I wanted to give back, both to New York --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 103380.0,
      "end_time": 107436.0,
      "text": "the city that allowed me the opportunity to follow my calling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107460.0,
      "end_time": 111140.0,
      "text": "but also to my origins and ancestors in Senegal."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 112460.0,
      "end_time": 115395.0,
      "text": "I wanted to contribute to that universal civilization"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 115420.0,
      "end_time": 116940.0,
      "text": "Senghor had described."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117700.0,
      "end_time": 120276.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t know how to make a measurable impact"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120300.0,
      "end_time": 121660.0,
      "text": "as a cook and writer."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123500.0,
      "end_time": 126796.0,
      "text": "While I was writing my first cookbook,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126820.0,
      "end_time": 131340.0,
      "text": "I often traveled to different regions of Senegal for research."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 132380.0,
      "end_time": 134516.0,
      "text": "During one of those trips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134540.0,
      "end_time": 137380.0,
      "text": "in the remote, southeast region of Kédougou"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 141620.0,
      "text": "I rediscovered an ancient grain called fonio"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 142500.0,
      "end_time": 146940.0,
      "text": "that had all but disappeared from the urban Senegalese diet."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148500.0,
      "end_time": 151356.0,
      "text": "It turns out that fonio had been cultivated"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 151380.0,
      "end_time": 153956.0,
      "text": "for more than five thousand years"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 153980.0,
      "end_time": 157739.0,
      "text": "and is probably the oldest cultivated cereal in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158580.0,
      "end_time": 161980.0,
      "text": "Once a popular grain on much of the continent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 162820.0,
      "end_time": 165700.0,
      "text": "fonio was grown all the way to ancient Egypt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 166500.0,
      "end_time": 171740.0,
      "text": "where archaeologists found grains inside pyramids&#39; burial grounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 172700.0,
      "end_time": 178435.0,
      "text": "Today it is mostly cultivated in the western part of the Sahel region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 178460.0,
      "end_time": 180756.0,
      "text": "from Senegal to Mali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180780.0,
      "end_time": 182760.0,
      "text": "Burkina Faso,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 182100.0,
      "end_time": 183540.0,
      "text": "Togo, Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 184900.0,
      "end_time": 190756.0,
      "text": "The Sahel region is that semiarid area south of the Sahara desert"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 190780.0,
      "end_time": 196100.0,
      "text": "that extends from the Atlantic in the west to the Red Sea in the east."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 197380.0,
      "end_time": 201760.0,
      "text": "I became more interested in this grain"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 201100.0,
      "end_time": 205180.0,
      "text": "that was deemed worth taking to the afterlife by early Egyptians."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 206940.0,
      "end_time": 209760.0,
      "text": "As I continued my research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 209100.0,
      "end_time": 213956.0,
      "text": "I found out that fonio was actually --"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 213980.0,
      "end_time": 215956.0,
      "text": "wherever it was cultivated --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 215980.0,
      "end_time": 219619.0,
      "text": "there was always some myth, or some superstition connected to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 220580.0,
      "end_time": 222360.0,
      "text": "The Dogon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 222600.0,
      "end_time": 223916.0,
      "text": "another great culture in Mali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 223940.0,
      "end_time": 225596.0,
      "text": "called it \"po,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225620.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "or, \"the seed of the universe.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 228300.0,
      "end_time": 230636.0,
      "text": "In that ancient culture&#39;s mythology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230660.0,
      "end_time": 234420.0,
      "text": "the entire universe sprouted from a seed of fonio."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 236260.0,
      "end_time": 239275.0,
      "text": "Aside from its purported mystical properties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 239300.0,
      "end_time": 241820.0,
      "text": "fonio is a miracle grain in many aspects."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 243340.0,
      "end_time": 244876.0,
      "text": "It is nutritious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 244900.0,
      "end_time": 248676.0,
      "text": "particularly rich in methionine and cysteine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 248700.0,
      "end_time": 253760.0,
      "text": "two amino acids that are deficient in most other major grains:"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 253100.0,
      "end_time": 256140.0,
      "text": "barley, rice or wheat to name a few."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 257339.0,
      "end_time": 258635.0,
      "text": "In addition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 258660.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261860.00000000003,
      "text": "fonio cultivation is great for the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 262580.0,
      "end_time": 264596.0,
      "text": "It tolerates poor soil"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 264620.0,
      "end_time": 266356.0,
      "text": "and needs very little water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 266380.0,
      "end_time": 268580.0,
      "text": "surviving where nothing else will grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 271500.0,
      "end_time": 272956.0,
      "text": "As a chef,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 272980.0,
      "end_time": 277900.0,
      "text": "what first struck me was its delicate taste and its versatility."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 279780.0,
      "end_time": 281299.0,
      "text": "Similar to couscous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 282820.0,
      "end_time": 286780.0,
      "text": "fonio has a delicious, nutty and earthy flavor."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 287900.0,
      "end_time": 290195.0,
      "text": "It can be turned into salad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 290220.0,
      "end_time": 292316.0,
      "text": "served as noodles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 292340.0,
      "end_time": 293955.0,
      "text": "used in baking"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 293980.0,
      "end_time": 299676.0,
      "text": "or simply as a substitute for any other grains in your favorite recipes."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 299700.0,
      "end_time": 306750.0,
      "text": "I am happy to share some of my fonio sushi and sweet potato sushi"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 306100.0,
      "end_time": 307460.0,
      "text": "with some of you right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 308220.0,
      "end_time": 310116.0,
      "text": "(Audience) Oh!"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 310140.0,
      "end_time": 312635.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 312660.0,
      "end_time": 313860.0,
      "text": "And okra."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 319300.0,
      "end_time": 321420.0,
      "text": "(Audience murmurs)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 323420.0,
      "end_time": 325116.0,
      "text": "In Kédougou"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 325140.0,
      "end_time": 327300.0,
      "text": "it is also nicknamed \"ñamu buur,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 328460.0,
      "end_time": 330955.0,
      "text": "which means \"food for royalty,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 330980.0,
      "end_time": 333220.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s served for guests of honor."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 333980.0,
      "end_time": 336660.0,
      "text": "Located at the border with Guinea and Mali,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 338460.0,
      "end_time": 341876.0,
      "text": "Kédougou first strikes visitors with its stunning vistas"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 341900.0,
      "end_time": 344179.0,
      "text": "and views of the Fouta Djallon Mountains."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 345200.0,
      "end_time": 350180.0,
      "text": "Sadly, it is also one of the poorest regions of Senegal."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 352140.0,
      "end_time": 355955.0,
      "text": "Because of desertification and lack of job prospects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 355980.0,
      "end_time": 359200.0,
      "text": "much of Kédougou&#39;s young population has left."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 360600.0,
      "end_time": 362996.0,
      "text": "They chose the deadly path of migration"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 363200.0,
      "end_time": 365460.0,
      "text": "in search of \"better\" opportunities."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 366740.0,
      "end_time": 367940.0,
      "text": "Often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 368860.0,
      "end_time": 371780.0,
      "text": "they risk their lives trying to reach Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 372900.0,
      "end_time": 375419.0,
      "text": "Some leave by crossing the Sahara desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 376380.0,
      "end_time": 379756.0,
      "text": "Others end up on inadequate wooden canoes"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 379780.0,
      "end_time": 382299.0,
      "text": "in desperate attempts to reach Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 384100.0,
      "end_time": 386716.0,
      "text": "According to a recent \"Guardian\" article,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 386740.0,
      "end_time": 392556.0,
      "text": "by 2020 more that 60 million people from sub-Saharan Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 392580.0,
      "end_time": 394916.0,
      "text": "are expected to migrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 394940.0,
      "end_time": 396876.0,
      "text": "due to desertification."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 396900.0,
      "end_time": 402756.0,
      "text": "This is the biggest global wave of migration since the Second World War,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 402780.0,
      "end_time": 404539.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s only set to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 405900.0,
      "end_time": 407260.0,
      "text": "So far this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 407980.0,
      "end_time": 412760.0,
      "text": "more that 2,100 migrants have lost their lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 412100.0,
      "end_time": 413700.0,
      "text": "on their way to Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 414900.0,
      "end_time": 417876.0,
      "text": "This is the reality of Kédougou"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 417900.0,
      "end_time": 419859.0,
      "text": "and of much of the Sahel today."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 421340.0,
      "end_time": 423195.0,
      "text": "Scary future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 423220.0,
      "end_time": 424996.0,
      "text": "scarce food"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 425200.0,
      "end_time": 428140.0,
      "text": "and no opportunities to change their situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 429860.0,
      "end_time": 432900.0,
      "text": "If life in your village weren&#39;t so precarious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 434260.0,
      "end_time": 437635.0,
      "text": "if there was a way to having enough food to get by,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 437660.0,
      "end_time": 439140.0,
      "text": "or having a paying job --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 440620.0,
      "end_time": 441956.0,
      "text": "if you and your sisters"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 441980.0,
      "end_time": 447316.0,
      "text": "didn&#39;t have to spend 30 percent of their waking hours"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 447340.0,
      "end_time": 448659.0,
      "text": "fetching water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 450600.0,
      "end_time": 452700.0,
      "text": "if conditions were just a little more hospitable ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 455620.0,
      "end_time": 458620.0,
      "text": "could the solution be right here in our soil?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 460100.0,
      "end_time": 462996.0,
      "text": "Could bringing fonio to the rest of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 463200.0,
      "end_time": 464219.0,
      "text": "be the answer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 466340.0,
      "end_time": 468476.0,
      "text": "Ancient grains are getting more popular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 468500.0,
      "end_time": 473276.0,
      "text": "and sales of gluten-free items are growing in the US --"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 473300.0,
      "end_time": 476516.0,
      "text": "16.4 percent since 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 476540.0,
      "end_time": 480700.0,
      "text": "making it a 23.3-billion-dollar industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 482780.0,
      "end_time": 485260.0,
      "text": "How could fonio partake in this market share?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 487780.0,
      "end_time": 490340.0,
      "text": "There are many challenges in turning fonio into food."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 491180.0,
      "end_time": 494636.0,
      "text": "Traditional processing is laborious and time-consuming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 494660.0,
      "end_time": 496900.0,
      "text": "especially when compared to other grains."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 500540.0,
      "end_time": 504540.0,
      "text": "Well, thankfully, technology has evolved."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 505340.0,
      "end_time": 507955.0,
      "text": "And there are now machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 507980.0,
      "end_time": 511596.0,
      "text": "that can process fonio in a more efficient way."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 511620.0,
      "end_time": 513996.0,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 514200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515635.00000000006,
      "text": "a few years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 515659.0,
      "end_time": 517116.0,
      "text": "Sanoussi Diakité,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 517140.0,
      "end_time": 518395.0,
      "text": "a Senegalese engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 518419.0,
      "end_time": 520635.0,
      "text": "won a Rolex prize"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 520659.0,
      "end_time": 524260.0,
      "text": "for his invention of the first mechanized fonio processor."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 525580.0,
      "end_time": 530475.0,
      "text": "Today, such machines are making life much easier for producers"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 530499.0,
      "end_time": 532180.0,
      "text": "around the whole Sahel region."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 534660.0,
      "end_time": 538915.0,
      "text": "Another challenge is the colonial mentality"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 538940.0,
      "end_time": 541660.0,
      "text": "that what comes from the west is best."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 543180.0,
      "end_time": 546195.0,
      "text": "This tendency to look down on our own products"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 546220.0,
      "end_time": 550556.0,
      "text": "and to see crops like fonio as simply \"country peoples&#39; food,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 550580.0,
      "end_time": 552436.0,
      "text": "therefore substandard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 552460.0,
      "end_time": 557596.0,
      "text": "explains why even though we don&#39;t produce wheat in Senegal traditionally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 557620.0,
      "end_time": 562760.0,
      "text": "it is far easier to find baguettes or croissants in the streets of Dakar"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 562100.0,
      "end_time": 564260.0,
      "text": "than it is to find any fonio products."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 566820.0,
      "end_time": 573196.0,
      "text": "This same mindset popularized the overprocessed, leftover rice debris"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 573220.0,
      "end_time": 575140.0,
      "text": "known as \"broken rice,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 576940.0,
      "end_time": 580476.0,
      "text": "which was imported to Senegal from Indochina"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 580500.0,
      "end_time": 582860.0,
      "text": "and introduced by the colonial French."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 585420.0,
      "end_time": 590156.0,
      "text": "Soon, broken rice became a key ingredient in our national dish,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 590180.0,
      "end_time": 591435.0,
      "text": "thiéboudienne,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 591460.0,
      "end_time": 596916.0,
      "text": "replacing our own traditional, more nutritious African rice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 596940.0,
      "end_time": 598180.0,
      "text": "Oryza glaberrima."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 599900.0,
      "end_time": 603795.0,
      "text": "Ironically, the same African rice despised at home"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 603820.0,
      "end_time": 605236.0,
      "text": "was hailed abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 605260.0,
      "end_time": 609276.0,
      "text": "Indeed, during the Atlantic slave trade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 609300.0,
      "end_time": 612859.0,
      "text": "this rice became a major crop in the Americas ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 614380.0,
      "end_time": 615915.0,
      "text": "particularly in the Carolinas"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 615940.0,
      "end_time": 618460.0,
      "text": "where it was nicknamed, \"Carolina gold.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 620460.0,
      "end_time": 621940.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s return to fonio."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 623660.0,
      "end_time": 628156.0,
      "text": "How can we turn its current status of \"country-people food\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 628180.0,
      "end_time": 630180.0,
      "text": "into a world-class crop?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 632380.0,
      "end_time": 633956.0,
      "text": "Last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 633980.0,
      "end_time": 638396.0,
      "text": "a business partner and I secured a commitment from Whole Foods Market,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 638420.0,
      "end_time": 641795.0,
      "text": "the US&#39;s largest natural food store chain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 641820.0,
      "end_time": 643200.0,
      "text": "to carry fonio."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 643820.0,
      "end_time": 648716.0,
      "text": "And we got a large American ingredient importer"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 648740.0,
      "end_time": 651756.0,
      "text": "interested enough to send a team of executives"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 651780.0,
      "end_time": 653596.0,
      "text": "to West Africa with us"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 653620.0,
      "end_time": 656100.0,
      "text": "to explore the supply chain&#39;s viability."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 658200.0,
      "end_time": 663156.0,
      "text": "We found ourselves observing manual operations"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 663180.0,
      "end_time": 665516.0,
      "text": "in remote locations"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 665540.0,
      "end_time": 667500.0,
      "text": "with few controls over quality."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 668620.0,
      "end_time": 671580.0,
      "text": "So we started focusing on processing issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 672780.0,
      "end_time": 674476.0,
      "text": "We drew up a vision"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 674500.0,
      "end_time": 679276.0,
      "text": "with a beneficial and commercially sustainable supply chain for fonio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 679300.0,
      "end_time": 682156.0,
      "text": "and we connected ourselves with organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 682180.0,
      "end_time": 683780.0,
      "text": "that can help us achieve it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 685180.0,
      "end_time": 688840.0,
      "text": "Walking backwards from the market, here is what it looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 689460.0,
      "end_time": 695716.0,
      "text": "Imagine that fonio is consumed all across the globe"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 695740.0,
      "end_time": 699380.0,
      "text": "as other popular ancient grains."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 701140.0,
      "end_time": 704196.0,
      "text": "Fonio touted on the levels of cereals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 704220.0,
      "end_time": 705836.0,
      "text": "breads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 705860.0,
      "end_time": 707600.0,
      "text": "nutrition bars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 708220.0,
      "end_time": 709916.0,
      "text": "cookies, pastas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 709940.0,
      "end_time": 711580.0,
      "text": "snacks -- why not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 712380.0,
      "end_time": 714396.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easier to say than quinoa."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 714420.0,
      "end_time": 716740.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 717660.0,
      "end_time": 722660.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 723900.0,
      "end_time": 725396.0,
      "text": "To get there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 725420.0,
      "end_time": 727836.0,
      "text": "fonio needs to be readily available"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 727860.0,
      "end_time": 730596.0,
      "text": "at a consistent quality for commercial users,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 730620.0,
      "end_time": 734436.0,
      "text": "such as food manufacturers and restaurant chains."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 734460.0,
      "end_time": 735940.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the part we&#39;re missing."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 736860.0,
      "end_time": 739916.0,
      "text": "To make fonio available at a consistent quality"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 739940.0,
      "end_time": 741676.0,
      "text": "for commercial use,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 741700.0,
      "end_time": 745116.0,
      "text": "you need a commercial-scale fonio mill"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 745140.0,
      "end_time": 748460.0,
      "text": "that adheres to international quality standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 749180.0,
      "end_time": 753360.0,
      "text": "Currently, there is no such mill in the whole world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 753600.0,
      "end_time": 754715.0,
      "text": "so in our vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 754740.0,
      "end_time": 759276.0,
      "text": "there is an African-owned and operated fonio mill"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 759300.0,
      "end_time": 761795.0,
      "text": "that processes efficiently"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 761820.0,
      "end_time": 767180.0,
      "text": "and in compliance with the requirements of multinational food companies."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 768180.0,
      "end_time": 773476.0,
      "text": "It is very difficult for the fonio producers today"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 773500.0,
      "end_time": 776360.0,
      "text": "to sell and use fonio"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 776600.0,
      "end_time": 779915.0,
      "text": "unless they devote a huge amount of time and energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 779940.0,
      "end_time": 783236.0,
      "text": "in threshing, winnowing and husking it."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 783260.0,
      "end_time": 784556.0,
      "text": "In our vision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 784580.0,
      "end_time": 787276.0,
      "text": "the mill will take on those tasks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 787300.0,
      "end_time": 793180.0,
      "text": "allowing the producers to focus on farming rather than processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 794220.0,
      "end_time": 798660.0,
      "text": "There is untapped agricultural capacity in the Sahel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 799820.0,
      "end_time": 802860.0,
      "text": "and all it takes is changing market conditions"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 803900.0,
      "end_time": 805699.0,
      "text": "to activate that capacity."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 806860.0,
      "end_time": 811676.0,
      "text": "By relieving fonio producers of manual operations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 811700.0,
      "end_time": 813996.0,
      "text": "the mill will free up their time"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 814200.0,
      "end_time": 818180.0,
      "text": "and remove the production bottleneck that limits their output."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 819100.0,
      "end_time": 821316.0,
      "text": "And there are other benefits as well"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 821340.0,
      "end_time": 825740.0,
      "text": "in using Sahel land for agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 827660.0,
      "end_time": 828860.0,
      "text": "More benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 829700.0,
      "end_time": 830980.0,
      "text": "higher employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 832100.0,
      "end_time": 835900.0,
      "text": "climate change mitigation by reversing desertification"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 837180.0,
      "end_time": 838739.0,
      "text": "and greater food security."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 839500.0,
      "end_time": 840860.0,
      "text": "Nice vision, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 841940.0,
      "end_time": 844100.0,
      "text": "Well, we are working towards getting it done."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 845600.0,
      "end_time": 849315.0,
      "text": "Last month we introduced fonio to shoppers in New York City"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 849340.0,
      "end_time": 850556.0,
      "text": "and online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 850580.0,
      "end_time": 856236.0,
      "text": "in a package that makes it attractive and desirable and accessible."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 856260.0,
      "end_time": 859460.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 863820.0,
      "end_time": 868516.0,
      "text": "We are talking with operators and investors in West Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 868540.0,
      "end_time": 870420.0,
      "text": "about building a fonio mill."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 871260.0,
      "end_time": 872876.0,
      "text": "And most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 872900.0,
      "end_time": 876760.0,
      "text": "we have teamed with an NGO called SOS SAHEL"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 876100.0,
      "end_time": 880996.0,
      "text": "to recruit, train and equip smallholders in the Sahel"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 881200.0,
      "end_time": 882900.0,
      "text": "to increase their fonio production."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 884420.0,
      "end_time": 887555.0,
      "text": "Hunger levels are higher in sub-Saharan Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 887580.0,
      "end_time": 890200.0,
      "text": "than any other place in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 891340.0,
      "end_time": 894756.0,
      "text": "The Sahel population is set to grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 894780.0,
      "end_time": 899339.0,
      "text": "from 135 million to 340 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 900140.0,
      "end_time": 904756.0,
      "text": "However, in that drought- and famine-prone region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 904780.0,
      "end_time": 906420.0,
      "text": "fonio grows freely."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 908180.0,
      "end_time": 910979.0,
      "text": "This tiny grain may provide big answers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 911780.0,
      "end_time": 914236.0,
      "text": "reasserting its Dogon name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 914260.0,
      "end_time": 917360.0,
      "text": "\"po,\" the seed of the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 917600.0,
      "end_time": 919236.0,
      "text": "and taking us one step closer"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 919260.0,
      "end_time": 921200.0,
      "text": "to the universal civilization."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 922340.0,
      "end_time": 923916.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 923940.0,
      "end_time": 927200.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}